"distributed to the bottom of the reactor. We hypothesize that the settled bed "
"will then break apart and settled into the band of fresh wastewater that is on "
"the bottom of the reactor. With this proposed mechanism it is clear that a "
"critical parameter is the depth of wastewater that should be injected with each "
"pulse. It is likely that this depth of fresh wastewater should be"
msgstr ""
